                    <p>
                        Using social media apps as part of a marketing campaign is known as "social media marketing."
                        Through social media, brands can:
                    </p>
                    <div class="card-theme">
                        <ul class="theme-list">
                            <li>Establish a brand;</li>
                            <li>Boost sales;</li>
